snippet.title: Rosemary Siemens
snippet.description:
Hi, I'm Rosemary Siemens! Welcome to my Inspirational YouTube Channel! I'm passionate about 'Bringing Back The Hymns' and I'm so excited to share my take on so many classic and inspired hymns with you! Every Sunday at 10am EST I premiere a new hymn video for my "Sunday Hymn Serenade" series along with an inspirational and uplifting story. I love connecting with you and taking requests and I hope you'll join me on my mission to 'Bring Back The Hymns'!

If you're interested, I have hymn CD's (and other styles) available for purchase, as well as sheet music and backing tracks available for my version of "Amazing Grace" and other hymns all available on my official website store!  All of the mp3's from my "Sunday Hymn Serenade" series and previous "Worship Wednesday" episodes are available for download or on CD via my Patreon!
